            Game Instructions

You will have to navigate through the Maze and answer questions

Each room will have doors in it.  These doors are locked with trivia questions.

In order to traverse the maze you will have to choose a direction, you can go to rooms
previously visited by clicking on the corresponding direction button.

The current question will not display until a direction with a question on it has been accessed.
Once this happens, a question will appear in the box to the left, and answer options will appear below it.

After you have answered the question click on the submit button.